      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several dents, fading paint, and areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several electronic components are currently non-functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs but has high mileage and is in need of immediate repairs to the suspension and exhaust system to be roadworthy. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the time and resources to invest in it.",
