      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion for your daily adventures? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and ready to get you where you need to go! It shows some signs of its travels and regular use, but it remains a practical and dependable choice that's perfect for anyone seeking great value and a solid ride. Come see why this road-tested gem is the perfect budget-friendly find!",
