    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom-ready condition, having been maintained with uncompromising attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care. For the discerning driver who demands the absolute best, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle of unparalleled quality and distinction.",
