      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an uncompromising example of the E46 M3, a vehicle that defines the analogue driving experience. This chassis is exceptionally tight, benefiting from a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul to ensure the S54 inline-six operates at peak volumetric efficiency. The engine bay is a testament to mechanical stewardship, featuring individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous transient response. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing has been inspected, and the suspension geometry is dialed in for maximum lateral grip. This is a turn-key, collector-grade machine with zero deferred maintenance and a valvetrain that sings all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 49250.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
